text: Mudarisovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Mikhaylovsky Selsoviet, Ufimsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 198 as of 2010. There are 14 streets. == Geography == It is located 15 km from Ufa, 9 km from Mikhaylovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ufimsky District
title: Mudarisovo
